libraries.name: Modelica
libraries.description: Free (standard conform) library from the Modelica Association to model mechanical (1D/3D), electrical (analog, digital, machines), thermal, fluid, control systems and hierarchical state machines. Also numerical functions and functions for strings, files and streams are included.

libraries.name: Modelica_DeviceDrivers
libraries.description: Free library for interfacing hardware drivers to Modelica models. There is support for joysticks, keyboards, UDP, TCP/IP, shared memory, AD/DA converters and other devices.

libraries.name: Modelica_LinearSystems2
libraries.description: Free library providing different representations of linear, time invariant differential and difference equation systems, as well as typical operations on these system descriptions.

libraries.name: Modelica_StateGraph2
libraries.description: Free library providing components to model discrete event, reactive and hybrid systems in a convenient way with deterministic hierarchical state diagrams. Modelica_StateGraph2 is not fully Modelica compliant and will never be, since a better solution is now available with Modelica 3.3

libraries.name: Modelica_Synchronous
libraries.description: Free (standard conform) library to precisely define and synchronize sampled data systems with different sampling rates. It provides convenient to use blocks to utilize the new synchronous language elements introduced in Modelica 3.3.

libraries.name: PowerSystems
libraries.description: Free (standard conform) library that is intended to model electrical power systems at different levels of detail both in transient and steady-state mode.

libraries.name: VehicleInterfaces
libraries.description: Free (standard conform) library from the Modelica Association for interface definitions and architectures for vehicle system modeling

libraries.name: ADGenKinetics
libraries.description: Modeling biochemical reaction networks with generalized kinetic formats with capabilities for computing parameter sensitivities using algorithmic differentiation techniques.

libraries.name: AixLib
libraries.description: A Modelica model library for building performance simulations

libraries.name: ATplus
libraries.description: Free library for Building Simulation and Building Control, fuzzy control library included. (unlicensed)

libraries.name: BioChem
libraries.description: BioChem is a package for biochemical modeling and simulation with Modelica

libraries.name: BondGraph
libraries.description: Free library for graphical Bond Graph modelling that contains common standard linear elements, sensors, and specific non-linear elements, especially for hydraulic networks.

libraries.name: BrineProp
libraries.description: Modelica.Media models for p-h-T-rho-eta properties of aqueous solutions of multiple salts (NaCl,KCl,CaCl2) and gases (CO2,N2,CH4). Two-phase model with VLE calculation.

libraries.name: modelica-buildings
libraries.description: Modelica Buildings library

libraries.name: Chemical
libraries.description: Modelica Library of Chemical and Electrochemical Processes

libraries.name: ComplexLib
libraries.description: Free library for steady-state analysis of AC circuits within phasor domain.

libraries.name: ExtendedPetriNets
libraries.description: Free library to model Petri nets and state transition diagrams (extended version).

libraries.name: ExternData
libraries.description: :page_facing_up: Modelica library for reading data from INI, JSON, XML and Excel XLS/XLSX files

libraries.name: FaultTriggering
libraries.description: Library for fault Modelling in Modelica

libraries.name: FCSys
libraries.description: Modelica fuel cell library

libraries.name: FuelCellLib
libraries.description: Free library to model fuel cells (unlicensed)

libraries.name: FuzzyControl
libraries.description: Free library for fuzzy control (unlicensed)

libraries.name: HelmholtzMedia
libraries.description: Modelica library for the calculation of fluid properties from a Helmholtz energy equation of state (EoS).

libraries.name: IdealizedContact
libraries.description: A Modelica library for idealized simulation of contact phenomena

libraries.name: IndustrialControlSystems
libraries.description: Modelica Industrial Control Systems Library by Politecnico di Milano

libraries.name: LinearMPC
libraries.description: Library for model-based predictive controllers with linear process models.

libraries.name: MotorcycleDynamics
libraries.description: Free library for the dynamic simulation of a motorcycle, and tailored to test and validation of active control systems for motorcycle dynamics.

libraries.name: MultiBondLib
libraries.description: Free library to model physical systems with multi-bond graphs.
